question: Joe probably was most likely visiting a family friend that was staying at the hotel.
answer:
Thank you anon for your thoughts. It is totally possible. 

Personally, when i’m walking by my parked car or my apartment, i always like to take a look, you know, to see how things are going. He didn’t. Not even a glance. You know, since there were so many fans this weekend in front of Taylor’s place, it’s impressive that he didn’t dare to take a look and see how things were going. And knowing how huge the loft is, i’m very very surprised Taylor didn’t make them stay with her.

summary: It actually makes me really sad that for whatever reason people think it’s ok to completely disrespect famous people such as...
body:
It actually makes me really sad that for whatever reason people think it’s ok to completely disrespect famous people such as Taylor Swift but not only her enough to stand outside of her home just to catch a glimpse of her.

Yes she’s famous, yes she’s on tour, yes she loves to meet her fans. But at the end of the day her and every other famous person out there are humans just like us. They deserve to leave their house without security having to hold back screaming crowds of fans and paparazzi.


It makes me so sad the videos being put up of people screaming and paparazzi with their cameras filming her, as the hurried to her car head down.


She loves her fans we love her I get that but surely our live for her can mean we can respect her privacy enough to let her live and leave in her own house in peace.


Sure some people may hate this post and some people may understand but at the end of the day she deserves respect and waiting for her outside her door is just not ok.

summary:
Hey Tay!💗💗💗
This is me, Rana. I am a swiftie since 2015 and maybe it’s not too long but I think it doesn’t matter💛 when I was...
caption:
Hey Tay!💗💗💗
This is me, Rana. I am a swiftie since 2015 and maybe it’s not too long but I think it doesn’t matter💛 when I was 5th grade (2015) my teacher made a English karaoke! And she said “everyone can join this, but of course who wants” anddd guess what, I was one of them! I was only person who joined to this show of my class. Then she gave me a paper and I saw your song, blank space!
The show day was coming up so fast. I remembered, I was so excited and can not wait it.
But the karaoke was started! My teacher calling to the other students. I was reeeeally so excited, my legs were trembling so hard. I was so scared. But then I thought “if Taylor was there, I know that she was gonna say to me that she wants to be calm down to me.” Then teacher invited me to the stage, and somehow the song started to play! And I started to singing. Eeeeeeveryone was looking at me. My friends, all the teachers, and there was a guy being there who was taking a picture or taking a video?!? At the end of my show, Everyone applauded me and I went to the my place quietly. I was feel so relaxed. That feels so good to me. I just could not sing it aloud when singing. But you know, I was proud of myself so much. I knew that if @taylorswift was there, we’ll be so proud of me together.
Then, a few days later, I learned that I was 3rd of this show. I was so shocked, I didn’t wait this. Then my teacher called me to the stage and she gave me a present. The present was a headphone. It looks so pretty and I’m already using!
I just want to say that, thanks for being in my life @taylorswift you are an amazing sister I’ve ever seen. Even if I sad, you make me so so better. And I hope that you’re having a good time. Because you are deserve to be happy. Love you!
-Rana💗

I just want to say that, thanks for being in my life @taylorswift you are an amazing sister I’ve ever seen. Even if I sad, you make me so so better. And I hope that you’re having a good time. Because you are deserve to be happy. Love you!
-Rana💗
